    <descript>
      <abstract>This dataset displays the topographical elevation lines above sea level in Prince William County. Descriptions for type codes can be found in the Prince William County Data Dictionary</abstract>
      <purpose>The purpose of this layer is to graphically show the topographical contour lines in Prince William County. These lines are record in 5-foot intermediate and 2.5 foot supplemental increments. Intermediate depressions are shown in multiples of 5 and Index depressions are in multiples of 25.</purpose>
      <supplinf>Any determination of topography or contours or any depiction of physical improvements, property lines or boundaries is for general information only and shall not be used for the design modification or construction of improvements to real property or for flood plain determination.</supplinf>
    </descript>
